###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  PRODUCTS (Admin only)
###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Product
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Wireless Headphones",
  "description": "High quality noise-cancelling headphones",
  "price": 99.99,
  "sku": "WH-001",
  "categoryId": null
}

### List Products
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/products

###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  INVENTORY (Admin only)
###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Add Inventory
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/inventory
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "productId": "ee04ec8d-a1a3-4941-9f78-6dd19dfdc381",
  "productName": "Wireless Headphones",
  "quantityToAdd": 100
}

### Check Stock
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/inventory/ee04ec8d-a1a3-4941-9f78-6dd19dfdc381

