###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  ORDERS — Place as Chandana (triggers email)
###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Step 3: Place Order — confirmation email sent to chandanacherry869@gmail.com
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "ee04ec8d-a1a3-4941-9f78-6dd19dfdc381",
      "productName": "Wireless Headphones",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 99.99
    }
  ]
}

### Cancel Order (PENDING only — paste order ID from Place Order response)
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get My Orders (as Chandana)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get Order by ID (as Chandana)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  ADMIN — All Orders (new endpoints)
###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get ALL orders from all users (paginated)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get all CONFIRMED orders
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/orders?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get all PENDING orders
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/orders?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get all CANCELLED orders
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/orders?status=CANCELLED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get any order by ID (admin can see any user's order)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  ADMIN — Own Orders
###  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Admin's own orders
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
